      "rationale": "Validation used the FDA generic pump geometry (not the actual VAD geometry) and a glycerol-water blood analog. Differences in geometry complexity and non-Newtonian blood rheology relative to the VAD COU are acknowledged but not formally quantified. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
