      "rationale": "Iterative convergence of residuals is reported but the impact of convergence tolerance on the hemolysis scalar QoI was not assessed. Round-off error analysis was not performed. Factor flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Use error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented review process ensuring correct model setup, boundary condition specification, and post-processing for each simulation run.",
      "rationale": "No formal use-error review protocol was implemented. Boundary condition setup was verified informally by the analyst only. Factor flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Justification for selection of turbulence model and hemolysis power-law model form; comparison of alternative model forms on hemolysis QoI.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on prior literature without systematic comparison of alternative turbulence closures on hemolysis prediction. Hemolysis power-law exponents taken from Giersiepen et al. without form uncertainty assessment. Factor flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
